In re Resignation of Hadley.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Hadley (1991), 59 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. 91-550 Submitted March 20, 1991 Decided March 27, 1991.)

The resignation of Walter F. Hadley, Jr. as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
